5:
Hmm... Should we get the chicken or
the pork?
10:
What's it matter? Everything here
tastes the same anyway, just hurry
up 'n pick!
15:
They DO go a bit overboard with the
seasoning here...
20:
Something odd is going on over
there...
24:
Hey little lady, what're you doin' all
alone here? Why don't you come
with us? We'll keep ya company.
26:
You're an adventurer, aren't you?
You'll get yourself killed jumpin' into
the Kaleidoscope all by your
lonesome. We'll escort ya!
33:
What a bunch of slimebags... We
should do something about this.
38: That's not all, Alk! Look closer.
41:
What's with those bangs, huh? Not
showing off those pretty eyes of
yours is such a waste! Come on,
don't be shy—
49: Yo! They're goin' after your stuff.
69: Hold on a second, I didn't—
78:
Take a deep breath, all right? Do you
hear me? Or rather, can you see me?
83:
Watch where you're swingin' that
damn thing already!
94:
So you mean to say... that you can't
look people in the eye?
98:
Y-yes. I don't know why, it's just...
terribly embarrassing for me.
103:
No need to be embarrassed!
Especially when you know your way
around a spear like that—wow.
106:
I can see my feet, so I usually just go
off that...
111:
You... can do all that by just looking
at your feet?! That is impressive.
114:
You can swing a stick around, yeah,
but you can't even tell who the hell
you're attacking! You didn't even
know those guys were tryin' to rob
you!
116: You might not be cut out for this, kid.
121: B-but... I don't want to give up!
124:
I want to overcome this! That's why...
that's why I'm wearing these clothes,
actually.
134:
My master told me to! He said that if
I wear these clothes, I'll never run out
of sparring partners—that way I'll be
able to overcome my shyness...
142:
He said it would draw people's
attention to me...
145:
I don't mind. Even if there's trouble, I
can just beat the crap out of them.
It's good practice.
153:
Yeah... I guess I'd be lying if I said it
didn't make me feel like I was being
used.
154:
I really can't stand the pervy grins
on people's faces either...
157:
But if that's what my master wishes,
then so be it. He's helped me out so
much, after all.
161:
You don't wanna do this, but you're
doin' it just cause this "master" of
yours says so?
162:
That sounds like a load of crap to
me.
175:
That brazen "I don't care" attitude...
your blunt way of speaking!
178: Are you tryin' to pick a fight here?
182:
Please teach me! Teach me how to
be rude and brash and to say what I
really think!
187:
Now that you mention it... If anyone
can teach you that, it's probably
Nimbus.
194:
C'mon now, you're givin' Stella the
final say?!
198:
We'd love to have you on the team,
Melmyna.
203:
There it is... I had a feelin' that was
gonna happen...
208:
Thank you so much! Mr. Nimbus, I'm
looking forward to learning from you!
212: I don't remember agreein' to this!
